==English==
{{Wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
From ''[[wiki]]'' + ''[[-pedia]]'', from English noun ''[[encyclopedia]]''.

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-Wikipedia.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Proper noun===
'''Wikipedia'''

# An open-content [[encyclopedia]], collaboratively developed over the [[Internet]], sponsored by the [[Wikimedia Foundation, Inc.]], and started in [[English]] on January 15, 2001.
# The staff of that encyclopedia.
# The article content of that encyclopedia.
#:'''quotations''':
#:"Work in the open-source software community or contribute to '''wikipedias''' on your favourite subjects." &mdash; ''[[w:Financial Times|Financial Times]]'', December 14, 2005
# A [[wiki]]
#:'''quotations''':
#:*"Just put it up on the web like a '''Wikipedia''' and let people add to it." &mdash; [[w:Thomas Friedman|Thomas Friedman]]



